import React, { useState } from "react";
import "../ComponentStyle/NavStyles.css";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

function Navbar() {
    const [clicked, setClicked] = useState(false);
    const handelClick = () => {
        setClicked({ clicked: !clicked });
        setClicked(!clicked);
    };
    return ( <
        >
        <
        nav >
        <
        Link to = "/hello" >
        <
        svg id = "logo-14"
        width = "73"
        height = "49"
        viewBox = "0 0 73 49"
        fill = "none"
        xmlns = "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" >
        { " " } <
        path d = "M46.8676 24C46.8676 36.4264 36.794 46.5 24.3676 46.5C11.9413 46.5 1.86765 36.4264 1.86765 24C1.86765 11.5736 11.9413 1.5 24.3676 1.5C36.794 1.5 46.8676 11.5736 46.8676 24Z"
        className = "ccustom"
        fill = "#68DBFF" >
        { " " } <
        /path>{" "} <
        path d = "M71.1324 24C71.1324 36.4264 61.1574 46.5 48.8529 46.5C36.5484 46.5 26.5735 36.4264 26.5735 24C26.5735 11.5736 36.5484 1.5 48.8529 1.5C61.1574 1.5 71.1324 11.5736 71.1324 24Z"
        className = "ccompli1"
        fill = "#FF7917" >
        < /path>{" "} <
        path d = "M36.6705 42.8416C42.8109 38.8239 46.8676 31.8858 46.8676 24C46.8676 16.1144 42.8109 9.17614 36.6705 5.15854C30.5904 9.17614 26.5735 16.1144 26.5735 24C26.5735 31.8858 30.5904 38.8239 36.6705 42.8416Z"
        className = "ccompli2"
        fill = "#5D2C02" >
        { " " } <
        /path>{" "} <
        /svg>{" "} <
        /Link>{" "} <
        div >
        <
        ul id = "navbar"
        className = { clicked ? "#navbar active" : "#navbar" } >
        <
        li > { " " } <
        Link className = "active"
        to = "/"
        style = {
            { textDecoration: "none" } } >
        { " " } <
        span > Home < /span>{" "} <
        /Link>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        li >
        <
        div class = "dropdown" >
        <
        Link class = "dropbtn" > Categories < i className = "fas fa-caret-down" > < /i></Link > { " " } <
        div class = "dropdown-content" >
        <
        li >
        <
        Link to = "/movies/bollywood" > Bollywood < /Link>{" "} <
        ul >
        <
        li >
        <
        a href = "/f" > Comedy < /a>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        li >
        <
        a href = "/f" > Action < /a>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        li >
        <
        a href = "/f" > Horror < /a>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        li >
        <
        a href = "/f" > Romance < /a>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        /ul>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        li >
        <
        Link to = "/movies/hollywood" > Hollywood < /Link>{" "} <
        ul >
        <
        li >
        <
        a href = "/f" > Resets < /a>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        li >
        <
        a href = "/f" > Resets < /a>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        li >
        <
        a href = "/f" > Resets < /a>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        /ul>{" "} <
        /li> <
        /div>{" "} <
        /div>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        li > { " " } <
        Link to = "/movies/popular"
        style = {
            { textDecoration: "none" } } > { " " } <
        span > Popular < /span>{" "} <
        /Link>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        li > { " " } <
        Link to = "/movies/toprated"
        style = {
            { textDecoration: "none" } } > { " " } <
        span > Top Rated < /span>{" "} <
        /Link>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        li > { " " } <
        Link to = "/movies/upcoming"
        style = {
            { textDecoration: "none" } } > { " " } <
        span > Upcoming < /span>{" "} <
        /Link>{" "} <
        /li>{" "} <
        /ul>{" "} <
        /div>{" "} <
        div id = "mobile"
        onClick = { handelClick } >
        <
        i id = "bar"
        className = { clicked ? "fas fa-times" : "fas fa-bars" } > { " " } <
        /i>{" "} <
        /div>{" "} <
        /nav>{" "} <
        />
    );
}

export default Navbar;
